FrontEnd for Tesseract OCR with simple image manipulation thru ImageMagick. 

1.- You need to have installed tesseract and ImageMagick

2.- Installation

   If you want to install it in your system executethe the next commands:

   $ sudo cp tesseract-gui.py /usr/local/bin
   $ sudo chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/tesseract-gui.py

3.- Use 
   
   If you have installed it in your system just run
   $ tesseract-gui.py

   Alternatively you can run it giving execution permisions and executing from the folder
   $ cd /path/to/folder
   $ chmod 755 tesseract-gui.py
   $ python tesseract-gui.py
   or
   $ ./tesseract-gui.py

   
   
